WEBVTT

00:00:57.360 --> 00:01:00.120
My mother is a Hindu,
and my father a Muslim.

00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:04.610
They probably did the first
battle for love of their time.

00:01:05.360 --> 00:01:08.056
They met in the small town of Aligarh,

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:11.400
fell in love and got married
in a couple of years.

00:01:11.920 --> 00:01:15.816
My two sisters and I led a strange life.

00:01:15.840 --> 00:01:18.936
Sometimes we were taken to shrines
to hear devotional music,

00:01:18.960 --> 00:01:20.736
